title: Save Your Life  -  Original Edition - REPOST
description:
had some difficulty sorry for reseed:

Here is the *original* version of the Save Your Life manual from the Richard Schulze
VHS series. This version is broken down by chapter and is a larger size to download. 

This was the first version before his name was deleted throughout the book and replaced by the word 'herbalist'. 


Warning: This information can cause leaps of faith and sustained attacks of personal responsibility. 


I have also posted the edited edition as it is smaller file size and for some people size really does matter

Be Well!

peace out.
